      "instruction": "<p>Reboil a kettle</p><p>Whilst the pasta is cooking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>salmon fillet[s] </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until browned on both sides and almost cooked through</p><p>Once browned, transfer to a plate and set aside for later</p>",
