    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p><p>Add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock </strong>to the pan and stir until the sauce begins to thicken</p>",
      "order": 5,
