    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove and discard the skin from the <strong>salmon</strong></p><p>Raise the heat to medium-high , then flake the<strong> salmon</strong> into the pan, then cook for 3-4 min or until the salmon is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked through when it's opaque and flakes easily</p>",
